# CareSense — Project Documentation

## 1. Overview

**CareSense** is an AI-powered **medical symptom checker and disease prediction web application**. A user selects the symptoms they are experiencing, provides context (duration and personal risk factors), and the system uses a trained ensemble of machine learning models to predict the most likely disease. It then delivers a full clinical-style report: disease description, medications, precautions, recommended diet, and lifestyle advice — all downloadable as a formatted PDF.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> CareSense is strictly an **educational and academic tool**. Its output does **not** constitute medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. It always advises consulting a licensed physician.

---

## 2. Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Web Framework | [Flask](https://flask.palletsprojects.com/) ≥ 2.3 |
| ML / Data | scikit-learn, pandas, NumPy |
| Visualization | Matplotlib, Seaborn |
| PDF Generation | ReportLab |
| Frontend | HTML5, CSS3, Vanilla JavaScript |
| Data Format | CSV (training & reference) + Pickle / JSON (model artifacts) |

