## 6. Web Pages

### [index.html](file:///c:/Users/hp/Documents/main%20projects/CareSense/templates/index.html) — Symptom Input
The main interface. Features:
- **Searchable symptom input** with autocomplete (calls `/autocomplete`)
- **Interactive body map** — click a body region to see related symptoms
- **Duration selector** per symptom (hours / days / weeks / chronic)
- **Risk factor panel** (age group, diabetic, smoker, hypertensive checkboxes)
- **Smart suggestions** shown dynamically as symptoms are selected
- Live prediction submitted via AJAX to `/predict`

### [result.html](file:///c:/Users/hp/Documents/main%20projects/CareSense/templates/result.html) — Diagnosis Result
Displays the complete diagnosis:
- Disease name + confidence badge + severity gauge
- Top-5 differential diagnosis probabilities
- Individual model votes (RF / SVM / NB)
- Symptom match breakdown (strong / moderate / weak / missing)
- Follow-up question panel (confirm or deny suggested key symptoms → calls `/followup`)
- Re-diagnose panel (add more symptoms → calls `/rediagnose`)
- Clinical info tabs: Description, Medications, Precautions, Diet, Workout
- **Download PDF** button (calls `/download_pdf`)

### [analytics.html](file:///c:/Users/hp/Documents/main%20projects/CareSense/templates/analytics.html) — Model Analytics
Displays all 9 training graphs and the [model_metrics.csv](file:///c:/Users/hp/Documents/main%20projects/CareSense/models/model_metrics.csv) table showing accuracy, F1, and CV scores for all 5 models.

### [diseases.html](file:///c:/Users/hp/Documents/main%20projects/CareSense/templates/diseases.html) — Disease Encyclopedia
Lists all 41 diseases with key symptoms, top frequent symptoms, medications, precautions, diets, and workouts. Also includes a full sortable symptom severity table.

### [awareness.html](file:///c:/Users/hp/Documents/main%20projects/CareSense/templates/awareness.html) — Health Awareness
Static health awareness content and articles.

