## 7. PDF Report Generation

When the user clicks **Download PDF**, [generate_pdf()](file:///c:/Users/hp/Documents/main%20projects/CareSense/app.py#867-1125) builds a multi-section A4 ReportLab document with:

| Section | Content |
|---|---|
| Cover Banner | Disease name, confidence, severity, timestamp |
| 1. Prediction Summary | Table of all key metrics |
| 2. Ensemble Model Votes | RF / SVM / NB individual predictions and agreement |
| 3. Differential Diagnosis | Embedded probability + symptom match bar chart (matplotlib) |
| 4. Symptom Match Analysis | Strong / Moderate / Weak / Missing table |
| 5. Severity & Confidence | Embedded gauge chart |
| 6. Reported Symptoms | Symptom + duration table |
| 7. About This Disease | Disease description paragraph |
| 8. Recommended Medications | Medication table |
| 9. Precautions | Bullet grid |
| 10. Recommended Diet | Bullet grid |
| 11. Lifestyle & Workout | Bullet grid |
| 12. How CareSense Works | Explanation table of ensemble/threshold logic |
| Footer | Medical disclaimer on every page |

